Pušioničar!

00:24:07.991 --> 00:24:09.868
Za ime Krista.

00:24:18.168 --> 00:24:20.212
Odlično.

00:24:26.176 --> 00:24:28.762
Ma daj me nemoj!

00:29:02.035 --> 00:29:04.037
Kretenčina!

00:30:38.090 --> 00:30:40.342
Pusti me na miru!

