obitelj bila retardirana.

00:32:08.638 --> 00:32:14.394
Genetski sjebani pubertetlija,
dupejebač!

00:32:14.394 --> 00:32:16.313
Maloga kurca.

00:32:19.524 --> 00:32:21.318
Znaš što?

00:32:21.318 --> 00:32:23.654
Dat ću ti ime.

